==== Crash Documentation

Participants (with parental assistance) will maintain electronic crash diaries including:
    - Date of crash trigger (exertion event)
    - Type of trigger (physical, cognitive, emotional, mixed)
    - Crash severity (1–10 scale, anchored descriptions)
    - Recovery duration (days to return to baseline)
    - Classification per crash severity tier (Table @tab:crash-severity-tiers from treatment chapter)

